Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(779,0)\fscy110\fsp-2.25\blur1.125\fs94.5\fnDay Roman\b1\an5\bord0\c&HF4F4F4&\pos(950.943,670.5)}A Saint's Agony ~ The Door of Faith Reopens ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.23,Blade,,0,0,0,,Queen's Blade:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:09.03,Blade,,0,0,0,,A quadrennial competition that determines the queen who rules the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.90,Blade,,0,0,0,,The newest queen abolished the royalty and brought equality to the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:18.95,Blade,,0,0,0,,Cities thrived, civilization improved, and people gained wealth and knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:26.33,Blade,,0,0,0,,However, this was the beginning of a very chaotic, anarchical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:45.98,Blade,,0,0,0,,This is the story of beautiful crusaders who fight for their beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.66,Blade,,0,0,0,,This shit is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.62,Blade,,0,0,0,,Goes down like water!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.04,Blade,,0,0,0,,Hey, more beer and beef! Make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:07.79,Blade,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord, I give thanks for tonight's generous bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:12.46,Blade,,0,0,0,,But God's a lazy-ass who can't be trusted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:19.72,Blade,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Like, no matter how much we pray, like, we're so normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.68,Blade,,0,0,0,,If it would make me strong right now, maybe I should just pray to Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:25.85,Blade,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:27.65,Blade,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.65,Blade,,0,0,0,,I will not tolerate any blasphemy against God!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:37.41,Blade,,0,0,0,,You wanna start something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,We were enjoying our drinks 'til you came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.12,Blade,,0,0,0,,Take responsibility, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:44.66,Blade,,0,0,0,,Stop this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:49.08,Blade,,0,0,0,,If you continue your trespasses against God, I shall condemn you as heretics!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.38,Blade,,0,0,0,,You could burn at the stake for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:55.88,Blade,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that? She's imitating the Inquisitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.47,Blade,,0,0,0,,Hilarious. She's just another powerless nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.85,Blade,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you now. You shall see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.89,Blade,,0,0,0,,Sacred pose–
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:15.11,Blade,,0,0,0,,No... wait... what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.03,Blade,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.49,Blade,,0,0,0,,You mocking us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,You guys are way too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.25,Blade,,0,0,0,,Let me eat my dinner in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.50,Blade,,0,0,0,,Sh-She was in the last Queen's Blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.29,Blade,,0,0,0,,That's Steel Princess Ymir, without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.17,Blade,,0,0,0,,I heard she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.05,Blade,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.42,Blade,,0,0,0,,They're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.47,Blade,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's flat as a board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.26,Blade,,0,0,0,,Who's that running their mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.51,Blade,,0,0,0,,St-Steel Princess Ymir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.05,Blade,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.22,Blade,,0,0,0,,You! You said you want to be stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.27,Blade,,0,0,0,,Then your best bet is to buy one of my prized weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.19,Blade,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Aren't they beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:56.86,Blade,,0,0,0,,For a limited time only, it's buy one, get one free!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.15,Blade,,0,0,0,,We-We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.74,Blade,,0,0,0,,Please pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Buy the weapons! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.70,Blade,,0,0,0,,Wait, your check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.83,Blade,,0,0,0,,Put it on our tab!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.62,Blade,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.92,Blade,,0,0,0,,I'm Shigi from the 16th monastery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:17.46,Blade,,0,0,0,,Our meeting here must be God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:23.64,Blade,,0,0,0,,You're such a reckless nun. To think you'd mess with those drunkards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.89,Blade,,0,0,0,,Punishing anyone who commits blasphemy against God is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:33.98,Blade,,0,0,0,,Are you a fundamentalist? By the way, weren't you trying to use the sacred power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:34.98,Blade,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.15,Blade,,0,0,0,,But I mess up every time I rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.95,Blade,,0,0,0,,Even though I finally received God's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.66,Blade,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:47.29,Blade,,0,0,0,,Those people should all burn at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.83,Blade,,0,0,0,,You're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:53.08,Blade,,0,0,0,,No, a seed of heresy should be crushed while it is still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.17,Blade,,0,0,0,,It would be bad for the believers if left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:02.22,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, that's that. So... wanna buy some weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.51,Blade,,0,0,0,,If you had my weapons, you'd be looked upon favorably during your propagations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.01,Blade,,0,0,0,,He has proclaimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:08.47,Blade,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:14.10,Blade,,0,0,0,,There shall be love and happiness for all believers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.90,Blade,,0,0,0,,But for the followers of Satan, there shall be only merciful, cleansing fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,Believe! Pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.36,Blade,,0,0,0,,Faith shall save all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like I've become involved with a real nutjob...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.24,Blade,,0,0,0,,His power is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.16,Blade,,0,0,0,,He is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:37.59,Blade,,0,0,0,,Oh, God. God, please bless us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:49.97,Blade,,0,0,0,,What nice weather. If this keeps up, maybe I can get there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.40,Blade,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.82,Blade,,0,0,0,,So you're also headed to Gainos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:08.74,Blade,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Central Holy Dynasty has commanded me to worship in the Grand Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.24,Blade,,0,0,0,,How about you, Ymir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.08,Blade,,0,0,0,,A business venture! I was thinking of selling these weapons to Claudette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.42,Blade,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.46,Blade,,0,0,0,,Queen Claudette is a great ruler...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.38,Blade,,0,0,0,,who generously protects the church and strengthens the power of the Holy Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.47,Blade,,0,0,0,,So these weapons will soon be used to spill the blood of heretics?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:33.56,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well... Maybe, maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:38.31,Blade,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Ymir! Let's exterminate the heretics together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.31,Blade,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.61,Blade,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.49,Blade,,0,0,0,,A child was suddenly struck by illness. It looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.95,Blade,,0,0,0,,Hold it together, Comse! Comse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.25,Blade,,0,0,0,,We sent for the town doctor, but I wonder if he'll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.59,Blade,,0,0,0,,Let's go. We can't do anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.63,Blade,,0,0,0,,Let us borrow His power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.13,Blade,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.96,Blade,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.14,Blade,,0,0,0,,Please do not worry. He will be well shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.61,Blade,,0,0,0,,Sacred pose: Healing.{Chiyu (Healing)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:54.56,Blade,,0,0,0,,God... please... save... this... child...{ Oh, God!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.02,Blade,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.50,Blade,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.08,Blade,,0,0,0,,Comse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.42,Blade,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.59,Blade,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.93,Blade,,0,0,0,,God be praised. His miracles are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.55,Blade,,0,0,0,,Maybe what's great here isn't God, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.31,Blade,,0,0,0,,your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:44.23,Blade,,0,0,0,,That "sacred pose"... You said last night that it doesn't work well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.15,Blade,,0,0,0,,but this time it worked just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:52.74,Blade,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is fine if I do not hurry, but I tend to fail at it when I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.66,Blade,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if someone draws a sword in front of you, that's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.95,Blade,,0,0,0,,To punish the heretics requires strength of mind as well as strength of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.12,Blade,,0,0,0,,That is why I learned martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.29,Blade,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:16.39,Blade,,0,0,0,,It's getting late. I thought we could get to Gainos by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:20.68,Blade,,0,0,0,,We decided to walk all night, but the road at night is kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:25.19,Blade,,0,0,0,,Do not fear, Ymir. God is with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.11,Blade,,0,0,0,,God might be with us, but snakes could be with us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.49,Blade,,0,0,0,,You sure seem happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.32,Blade,,0,0,0,,Of course! With this, I can burn any heretics at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:44.21,Blade,,0,0,0,,I hear that there are bandits around here. Perhaps a traveler is being robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.46,Blade,,0,0,0,,Bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.67,Blade,,0,0,0,,To think that they would rob a genuine believer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.00,Blade,,0,0,0,,This is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.13,Blade,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ymir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.96,Blade,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.84,Blade,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna get involved in a skirmish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.80,Blade,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, if that traveler had my weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.56,Blade,,0,0,0,,he could have easily defeated the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.52,Blade,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Don't take the fire with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.65,Blade,,0,0,0,,S-Snakes might come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.04,Blade,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me. I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.25,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well then, just leave your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.54,Blade,,0,0,0,,I might just have to split you in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.21,Blade,,0,0,0,,Stop this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.38,Blade,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.68,Blade,,0,0,0,,A servant of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.31,Blade,,0,0,0,,What you are doing, ganging up on an innocent old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.60,Blade,,0,0,0,,It is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.93,Blade,,0,0,0,,Whew, I finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:50.36,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, one, two, three... Wow, there's so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! I have some exciting news!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.45,Blade,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that even bandits like you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.03,Blade,,0,0,0,,have heard about the Steel Princess's rare weapons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:02.83,Blade,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.45,Blade,,0,0,0,,Let's kill her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.21,Blade,,0,0,0,,Those dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.83,Blade,,0,0,0,,I haven't even got to the meat of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:13.05,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll just have to show them the power of my weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.68,Blade,,0,0,0,,Ymir, I will fight, too. I must punish these insolent men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.85,Blade,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.27,Blade,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.69,Blade,,0,0,0,,Use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:31.90,Blade,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.48,Blade,,0,0,0,,You guys are new to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.96,Blade,,0,0,0,,Hold on there. You can't fight with those, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:50.92,Blade,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna buy these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.60,Blade,,0,0,0,,How the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.10,Blade,,0,0,0,,Time for your punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.73,Blade,,0,0,0,,The sword... I want the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.15,Blade,,0,0,0,,This is for the ax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,Give me a shield, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.99,Blade,,0,0,0,,Let's do this like gentlemen. Line up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.78,Blade,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.12,Blade,,0,0,0,,Wait, let me have the sword instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.37,Blade,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,Don't forget my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.00,Blade,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.79,Blade,,0,0,0,,Such wealthy bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.46,Blade,,0,0,0,,I haven't made a profit like this in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.67,Blade,,0,0,0,,It was a good idea to give her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.52,Blade,,0,0,0,,This sword is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.85,Blade,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I like that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.78,Blade,,0,0,0,,This will FINISH you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:05.03,Blade,,0,0,0,,Do not underestimate God's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.25,Blade,,0,0,0,,His protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.75,Blade,,0,0,0,,That looks painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.21,Blade,,0,0,0,,I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.55,Blade,,0,0,0,,I'm next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.05,Blade,,0,0,0,,No, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.18,Blade,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.97,Blade,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.77,Blade,,0,0,0,,Why are you guys having such a hard time against a lone nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.23,Blade,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.70,Blade,,0,0,0,,You're the leader of these ruffians?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.03,Blade,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:49.03,Blade,,0,0,0,,Pray. Beg for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.37,Blade,,0,0,0,,Even though you became a bandit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:56.88,Blade,,0,0,0,,if you change your ways and promise to follow God, He shall forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.88,Blade,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:03.38,Blade,,0,0,0,,The only people that benefit from a god are people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:08.43,Blade,,0,0,0,,God is absolute. If you do not obey, you will be regarded as a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.06,Blade,,0,0,0,,A heretic? Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:18.44,Blade,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, I actually feel closer to Satan than God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,Such heretical words...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,You shall know your place. Sacred pose:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.37,Blade,,0,0,0,,Re... morse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.66,Blade,,0,0,0,,No, not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.08,Blade,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,Close my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.67,Blade,,0,0,0,,Sacred pose: Remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.75,Blade,,0,0,0,,It's not working...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.63,Blade,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.89,Blade,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of sparing your life if you stripped yourself naked,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.51,Blade,,0,0,0,,but I don't feel like it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.19,Blade,,0,0,0,,God will never desert a believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:03.36,Blade,,0,0,0,,We'll see if you still feel that way after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.79,Blade,,0,0,0,,How are you going to fight against this many men?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.42,Blade,,0,0,0,,Pray if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.67,Blade,,0,0,0,,But you will die all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.85,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, well. This is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.02,Blade,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:38.60,Blade,,0,0,0,,So this is the true strength of the bandits' leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.02,Blade,,0,0,0,,But I don't know about that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.19,Blade,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:46.40,Blade,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the best of the best:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,The sword that the champion of the last Queen's Blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.49,Blade,,0,0,0,,Leina, also used: the Ewindel Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:57.08,Blade,,0,0,0,,Wow! {\i1}The{\i0} wandering warrior's sword? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:02.38,Blade,,0,0,0,,If you wanna deliver the final blow, you should at least use a sword of this caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.54,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, it's sorta expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.26,Blade,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the price. I'll buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.51,Blade,,0,0,0,,It's a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.55,Blade,,0,0,0,,I bought you some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:18.10,Blade,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you. Brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.78,Blade,,0,0,0,,Have you finished your final prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:32.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,God is absolute. Believers always achieve victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.45,Blade,,0,0,0,,Then pray and die where you stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.41,Blade,,0,0,0,,Believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.62,Blade,,0,0,0,,Entrust Him with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.79,Blade,,0,0,0,,Sacred pose: Worship.{"Reibai" (praying).}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:37.97,Blade,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you, Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.73,Blade,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd change...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,from something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.83,Blade,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.80,Blade,,0,0,0,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.48,Blade,,0,0,0,,Phew, we've finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.40,Blade,,0,0,0,,So this is Gainos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.11,Blade,,0,0,0,,You were pretty harsh back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.66,Blade,,0,0,0,,I thought you had forgiven them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.91,Blade,,0,0,0,,But you still burned them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, they {\i1}were{\i0} heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:49.21,Blade,,0,0,0,,Burning heretics is His love; His way of purifying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.17,Blade,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.34,Blade,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.51,Blade,,0,0,0,,It was a pretty fun journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.43,Blade,,0,0,0,,Same here. Thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.39,Blade,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.86,Blade,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.90,Blade,,0,0,0,,Payment for that weapon I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.49,Blade,,0,0,0,,You're... charging me for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:25.37,Blade,,0,0,0,,Obviously. I'm Steel Princess Ymir, don't ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.84,Blade,,0,0,0,,You seem to be prepared, Shigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.84,Blade,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:43.22,Blade,,0,0,0,,Then, in the name of God and the Central Holy Dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.10,Blade,,0,0,0,,I hereby designate you as the Inquisitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.02,Blade,,0,0,0,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.90,Blade,,0,0,0,,As the Inquisitor, I proclaim:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:03.87,Blade,,0,0,0,,All heretics and sinners shall be burned at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.12,Blade,,0,0,0,,Sacred pose:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.46,Blade,,0,0,0,,Fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.30,Blade,,0,0,0,,Who will the goddess of victory favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.98,Blade,,0,0,0,,Whose beliefs will prevail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.57,Blade,,0,0,0,,Only battles will determine the winner.
